'''Oliver Ford Davies''' (born [[August 12]], [[1930s|1939]]) played [[Governor of Naboo|Governor]] [[Sio Bibble]] in [[Star Wars: Episode I The Phantom Menace|''The Phantom Menace'']], [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'']], and [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Revenge of the Sith'']]. He appeared alongside [[Ewan McGregor]] in an episode of the crime drama [[Wikipedia:Kavanagh QC|''Kavanagh QC'']] in [[1995]].

Oliver Ford Davies also worked with [[George Lucas]] on Lucas's [[1992]] television series [[Wikipedia:The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles|''The Young Indiana Jones Chronicles'']], in which he was credited as "Ship's Captain" in the pilot movie ''Young Indiana Jones and the Curse of the Jackal''. In [[1991]], he appeared alongside [[Kenneth Colley]] in the ''Inspector Morse'' episode ''Second Time Around''.

